something might've happened to you, too!

00:02:09.290 --> 00:02:10.110
What?

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:11.780
Then this thing...

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:14.930
Anyway, just be careful.

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:16.130
