00:08:26.910 --> 00:08:28.570
Hey, move!

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:34.150
What?! It can't be...

00:08:34.380 --> 00:08:38.750
So one of these guys just has 
to glance at your back, right?

00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:40.970
My ability is only to speak.

00:08:40.970 --> 00:08:45.500
But, you see, humans aren't the 
only ones that I can talk to.

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:48.880
I'm the one who called them here.

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:50.600
They hate you.

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:55.620
