00:09:09.370 --> 00:09:10.550
I won!

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:12.980
3 Freeze!

00:09:14.490 --> 00:09:17.130
These animals didn't do anything wrong.

00:09:17.130 --> 00:09:20.580
So scram, all of you. Shoo.

00:09:20.580 --> 00:09:22.550
Th-That Stand is...

00:09:23.500 --> 00:09:24.430
Koichi!

00:09:24.430 --> 00:09:25.690
What?!

00:09:25.940 --> 00:09:28.400
I thought that you might 
just be messing with me,

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:30.830
but I was still a bit worried, so I went back,

00:09:30.830 --> 00:09:33.330
and you were still acting 
weird, Rohan-sensei.

00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:35.720
Even outside your house, you were 
walking with your back to walls,

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:39.600
and crossing the street with your 
back to someone else's, all by yourself.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:42.460
So you really do have an 
enemy Stand on your back.

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:47.350
That's exactly what I admire 
so much about you...

00:09:47.610 --> 00:09:49.810
You truly are my friend.

00:09:50.130 --> 00:09:51.580
It's on your back, right?

00:09:51.580 --> 00:09:54.830
I just have to remove the 
enemy from your back, right?

00:09:59.340 --> 00:10:02.910
Reverb, 3 Freeze!

00:10:05.330 --> 00:10:06.560
Heavy...

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.370
