Huh?!

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:30.330
Go ahead and tell Koichi, okay? 
Hurry up and tell him!

00:10:30.330 --> 00:10:32.320
R-Rohan-sensei?!

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:33.980
K-Koichi...

00:10:34.220 --> 00:10:38.820
I'm very moved that you came 
here, and very grateful...

00:10:38.820 --> 00:10:42.410
But I'd appreciate it if you'd withdraw Act 3.

00:10:43.010 --> 00:10:47.950
You can't see it, but my back is 
starting to rip ever so slightly...

00:10:49.740 --> 00:10:52.870
Act 3! Undo the 3 Freeze!

00:10:52.870 --> 00:10:55.510
S-h-i-t. Understood.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:59.590
R-Rohan-sensei! A-Are...

00:10:59.590 --> 00:11:02.500
Of course I'm not okay, Koichi Hirose!

00:11:02.500 --> 00:11:05.350
This damage is your fault, isn't it?

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:09.120
Do you get it now? 
There's no way to get rid of me.

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:11.670
Peeling me off your back, Rohan,

00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:15.200
