00:16:19.290 --> 00:16:20.280
Forgive you?

00:16:20.520 --> 00:16:22.190
Now, wait a minute.

00:16:23.030 --> 00:16:26.080
I'm not angry or anything.

00:16:26.530 --> 00:16:28.050
This is something I enjoy.

00:16:28.370 --> 00:16:30.900
I chose you because you 
suited my taste, as well.

00:16:30.900 --> 00:16:35.580
I was born with these tastes, so I'm just 
trying to act positively about it.

00:16:35.850 --> 00:16:37.190
Positively...

00:16:37.860 --> 00:16:40.670
It sounded like you were asking 
your boyfriend for some earrings.

00:16:40.670 --> 00:16:42.950
Here, he left these for you.

00:16:43.200 --> 00:16:44.710
It's a present.

00:16:49.190 --> 00:16:54.120
You're very good at cutting nails. 
I like that about you, too.

00:16:57.600 --> 00:17:01.210
And you are truly adorable 
when you don't talk.

00:17:01.830 --> 00:17:04.330
What to do, Minako...

00:17:04.330 --> 00:17:06.630
I want to take you home with me,

00:17:07.060 --> 00:17:10.120
but bringing you into the 
Kawajiri home would be risky.

00:17:10.120 --> 00:17:15.080
Still, this is refreshing... 
This is truly refreshing!

00:17:18.900 --> 00:17:22.890
Th-The man and woman he 
followed from the station...

00:17:23.120 --> 00:17:25.320
He killed them and made them disappear!

00:17:37.410 --> 00:17:39.460
That's... Hayato.

00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:42.370
What is he doing in a place like this?

00:17:42.710 --> 00:17:46.040
This is the opposite direction 
from the house and his school...

00:17:47.170 --> 00:17:47.970
What's that?

00:17:52.940 --> 00:17:55.140
I didn't lock the door...

00:17:57.110 --> 00:17:59.430
Hayato... He...

00:18:02.920 --> 00:18:04.290
It couldn't be.

00:18:07.280 --> 00:18:11.700
He's not human... What is that 
thing that's disguised as my dad?

00:18:29.700 --> 00:18:31.880
There's evidence that they've been back here.

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:34.060
And there are blood stains on the floor.

00:18:37.170 --> 00:18:39.790
Did he finally make his move?

00:18:46.680 --> 00:18:50.650
July 15th (Thurs)  8:36 PM

00:18:53.100 --> 00:18:58.480
The thing in Hayato's hand 
was definitely a handy cam.

00:19:00.390 --> 00:19:02.740
It doesn't seem to be in 
this room right now...

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:04.740
Hayato...

00:19:05.040 --> 00:19:07.480
He's been acting weird 
ever since the other day.

00:19:07.840 --> 00:19:11.870
I have to find out what Hayato was doing.

00:19:12.380 --> 00:19:14.390
I have to find out for sure.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:16.510
C-Calm down...

00:19:16.890 --> 00:19:19.770
I have to calm down and gather my thoughts.

00:19:23.300 --> 00:19:25.610
First, this videotape...

00:19:26.480 --> 00:19:28.770
Should I show it to someone?

00:19:29.470 --> 00:19:30.760
I can't show it to Mom!

00:19:30.980 --> 00:19:33.280
Mom totally trusts him.

00:19:33.560 --> 00:19:35.450
Should I show it to the police?

00:19:35.820 --> 00:19:40.010
Would they believe that a person got 
blown up and then disappeared?

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:43.630
More importantly, he's not human...

00:19:43.920 --> 00:19:47.040
Could the police even 
catch someone like him?

00:19:47.040 --> 00:19:51.580
No... Does anyone even exist in 
this world who could catch him?

00:19:51.580 --> 00:19:52.680
What should I do?

00:19:52.680 --> 00:19:55.470
Mom and I are going to be killed eventually.

00:19:56.190 --> 00:19:58.010
What am I supposed to do?!

00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:07.520
Do you mind if I join you...

00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:11.850
in the bath, Hayato?

00:20:13.540 --> 00:20:16.140
It's been a while.

00:20:20.310 --> 00:20:22.650
I-I'm gonna head out now.

00:20:22.650 --> 00:20:24.180
Oh, come on.

00:20:24.180 --> 00:20:27.660
We're family, after all...

00:20:28.400 --> 00:20:30.950
Wh-What does he want?

00:20:30.950 --> 00:20:33.250
I'll be in trouble if he finds this tape.

00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:38.140
I'm sorry, Hayato, but could 
you let go of the bucket?

00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:41.590
I want to draw some water and wash my body.

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:46.210
I-I'll wash your back for you, Dad!

00:20:47.740 --> 00:20:49.910
That's a great idea.

00:20:51.140 --> 00:20:54.230
But I'll wash your back first.

00:20:55.340 --> 00:21:01.000
You're the one who got in first. 
I'll wash yours first, then we can switch.

00:21:01.700 --> 00:21:03.560
Now, sit down.

00:21:11.900 --> 00:21:16.110
What's the matter? 
You seem to be sweating quite a bit.

00:21:16.110 --> 00:21:17.120
Did you get get too hot?

00:21:17.120 --> 00:21:17.930
Y-Yeah...

00:21:18.120 --> 00:21:21.180
Then why are you shivering?

00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:26.250
Isn't it strange to shiver if you're overheated?

00:21:26.950 --> 00:21:28.940
You're tickling me, Dad!

00:21:28.940 --> 00:21:33.160
You should know that I've 
always been ticklish!

00:21:35.890 --> 00:21:37.960
You're... right.

00:21:38.620 --> 00:21:41.930
You've always been ticklish, Hayato.

00:21:41.930 --> 00:21:44.590
I-I'll wash my front...

00:21:44.590 --> 00:21:46.700
I see. So you'll do it yourself.

00:21:48.980 --> 00:21:52.160
By the way, I just remembered...

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:53.450
This evening,

00:21:53.450 --> 00:21:58.000
I was around the Jozenji area that's 
in the opposite direction from home,

00:21:58.000 --> 00:21:59.520
and I saw you.

00:21:59.520 --> 00:22:00.390
Huh?!

00:22:00.890 --> 00:22:02.890
With a video camera!

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:05.040
What were you doing?

00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:07.390
Now I know for sure!

00:22:07.900 --> 00:22:11.140
This little brat was watching!

00:22:11.590 --> 00:22:16.680
This is awful... I thought I'd 
peacefully fit into this household...

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:18.900
I've had nothing but misfortune this year.

00:22:19.280 --> 00:22:20.760
What an awful year.

00:22:21.400 --> 00:22:25.280
Killing this brat will draw attention 
to myself, and that would be very bad.

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:28.820
But since he saw that, I have no choice!

00:22:30.080 --> 00:22:33.870
I just turned one of the strands 
of this brat's hair into a bomb.

00:22:33.870 --> 00:22:36.790
If I just cause a slight explosion on his head,

00:22:36.790 --> 00:22:40.090
it'll just look like he slipped 
and hit his head on the bath.

00:22:40.090 --> 00:22:42.090
That's a common accident in our society.

00:22:42.090 --> 00:22:43.300
You're going to die.

00:22:43.300 --> 00:22:44.840
Die, brat!

00:22:44.840 --> 00:22:46.710
Are you going to kill me, too?

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:50.420
Even though I've got video of you...

00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:52.880
I'm even videotaping you right now!

00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:53.690
What?

00:22:57.260 --> 00:22:59.480
I've been suspicious of you this whole time.

00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:00.520
Your different shoe size

00:23:00.520 --> 00:23:03.230
and the fact that you were practicing 
your signature are all on tape!

00:23:03.230 --> 00:23:05.100
I've got other tapes, too!

00:23:05.100 --> 00:23:07.620
I even took a video of the cat-like 
plant you've got in the attic!

00:23:08.320 --> 00:23:11.080
I'm the only one who knows 
where the tapes are!

00:23:11.290 --> 00:23:15.580
But if something were to happen to me, 
I'm sure someone would find that place.

00:23:15.760 --> 00:23:17.210
What?

00:23:17.550 --> 00:23:20.080
Don't you dare lay a finger on me! Got it?

00:23:20.460 --> 00:23:25.210
You little shit! You dare threaten me?

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:27.680
I won't let you touch my mom, either!

